    "long_instructions": "### Layering Multiple Backtracks with Loops\r\n\r\nLet's extend these tracks for a live performance and add use triggers to add the final vocal and claps to our song!\r\n\r\n- Extend the loops so the song is at least 30 measures long\r\n- Use `Trigger 1` to play the last vocal on the next beat\r\n- Use `Trigger 2` to play the clap effect immediately\r\n\r\n**Run Your Code!** Use triggers to improvise in the moment!",
